Package: PeakGuideR
Title: Evidence-Based Annotation of MALDI-MSI Metabolites Features
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(
    given= "Nadia", 
    family= "Molto", 
    email= "nadia.molto@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID= "0009-0003-0042-4997")))
Description: Provides tools for evidence-based annotation of MALDI mass spectrometry imaging features from peak matrix data. PeakGuideR integrates isotope morphology detection, 
    carbon isotope-ratio validation, elemental isotope-pattern support, adduct-family detection, and optional neutral-mass database matching.
    Optional compound and strandard-adduct databases included with the package are intended for non-comercial research use and may be subject to third party data licencing terms.
URL: https://github.com/nadiamolto/PeakGuideR, https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.20705395, https://nadiamolto.github.io/PeakGuideR/
